GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 18th November, 2005
27 Kartika, 1927(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 18th
November, 2005-
Shri S. Jaipal Reddy relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Information & Broadcasting and assumed the charge of
the office of the Minister of Urban Development. He will continue to
hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Culture;
i)
Shri Priya Ranjan Dasmunsi relinquished the charge of the office of
the Minister of Water Resources and assumed the charge of the
office of Minister of Information & Broadcasting. He will continue to
hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Parliamentary Affairs;
ii)
iii)
Shri Sontosh Mohan Dev assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Water
Resources. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the
Minister of Heavy Industry & Public Enterprises; and
Shri Oscar Fernandes assumed the charge of the office of the
Minister of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Youth
Affairs & Sports and the office of the Minister of State (Independent
Charge) of the Ministry of Overseas Indian Affairs. He will continue
to hold the charge of the Minister of Statistics & Programme
Implementation.
iv)
(K.L. Sharma)
